				<h2>Interior / Salon</h2>
				<p class="s-equip__note">3-Cabin Owner's Version. 6'3" minimum headroom throughout. Custom upholstery and interior finishings.</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Mabru Air Conditioner 12,000 BTU plumbed to Master Cabin and Salon — High Efficiency 12V DC, Soft Start (May 2022)</li>
					<li>Mabru Air Conditioner 17,000 BTU 120V plumbed to Port hull and Salon (June 2024) <span class="s-equip__badge s-equip__badge--new">New</span></li>
					<li>Samsung Automatic Washing Machine</li>
					<li>Samsung Smart TV with 12v Boost Antenna</li>
					<li>BOSS 12v Radio / Sound System with CD, USB and Bluetooth</li>
					<li>Amplifier (Feb 2023)</li>
					<li>2 x BOSS 6x9 Saloon Speakers</li>
					<li>2 x Skar Speakers Facing Stern (Feb 2023)</li>
					<li>2 x JBL Wake Tower Speakers added to Mast Spreader (Oct 2023)</li>
					<li>2 x Skar 6" Cockpit Speakers in Travelers Arch (Feb 2023)</li>
					<li>Re-upholstered couches and bar stools throughout vessel</li>
					<li>10 x Seating Blue Sunbrella Upholstered Settee (Feb 2022)</li>
					<li>4 x Movable Blue Sunbrella Upholstered Bar Stools (Feb 2022)</li>
					<li>3 x Movable Blue Sunbrella Upholstered Lower Stools (Feb 2022)</li>
					<li>Coffee Table with Corian Worktop</li>
					<li>Bar top with stool seating for 4</li>
					<li>Corian Work Surfaces</li>
					<li>Storage Underneath Settee Seating</li>
					<li>4 x Storage cabinets with Sliding Door — Smoked Perspex</li>
					<li>NAV / Chart Table with storage underneath</li>
					<li>A/C Breaker and Indicator Panels at NAV Station</li>
					<li>Steering System, 12V and AC Component Access Panels Below NAV station</li>
					<li>Escape hatch located in Main Center Forward Salon</li>
					<li>Overhead and Bulkhead Mounted LED Spot Lights (White or Red)</li>
					<li>New Salon Lighting/Fixtures</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- MASTER CABIN -->
			<div class="s-equip__section" id="master">
				<h2>Master Cabin (Starboard Hull)</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Queen Bed with New Serta Mattress (2022) — enough space for a King mattress if desired <span class="s-equip__badge s-equip__badge--new">New</span></li>
					<li>Hanging and Storage Cupboards with Shelves</li>
					<li>Bedside Bookshelf / Storage Locker</li>
					<li>Full Length Dressing Mirror</li>
					<li>LED Reading and Overhead Lights</li>
					<li>2 x Circulation Fans</li>
					<li>2 x Overhead Opening Hatches</li>
					<li>Stainless Steel Clothes and Towel Rail</li>
					<li>Remote Generator Start / Stop</li>
					<li>Large Head with spacious separate shower stall</li>
					<li>Dometic Masterflush electric head (2025)</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- GUEST CABINS -->
			<div class="s-equip__section" id="guest">
