				<ul>
					<li>2 x Queen size Custom Beds with Split mattresses</li>
					<li>2 x Ensuite Heads with Jabsco Quiet Flush Electric Toilets</li>
					<li>2 x Pressurized Hot and Cold fresh water Showers and Sinks</li>
					<li>2 x Integrated hand basins with Extendable Mixer</li>
					<li>2 x Vanity Cabinet with Mirror and Stainless Steel Towel Rails</li>
					<li>2 x Toiletries Storage Cupboards</li>
					<li>2 x Dressing Mirrors</li>
					<li>Hanging and Storage Cupboards with Shelves</li>
					<li>Storage/Book Shelves</li>
					<li>LED Overhead Lights</li>
					<li>Red LED night lights in Heads</li>
					<li>LED Bulkhead Mounted Reading Lights</li>
					<li>12v Ventilation Fans</li>
					<li>Large Overhead Opening Hatches with Nicro Solar Ventilation Fans</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- GALLEY -->
			<div class="s-equip__section" id="galley">
				<h2>Galley</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>12v Adler Barbour Freezer — XL with two access doors, air-cooled, digital control</li>
					<li>12v Adler Barbour Refrigerator with Digital Controls</li>
					<li>Alpes Inox Propane Stove — 4 burner stainless steel</li>
					<li>Alpes Inox Propane Oven with Fan-Driven Air Circulation and Electric Rotisserie</li>
					<li>Sharp Convection Microwave</li>
					<li>Corian Work Surfaces with Stainless Steel Rails and Fiddles</li>
					<li>Pressurized Hot and Cold fresh Water</li>
					<li>Salt Water spigot</li>
					<li>Hand Operated Emergency Water Pump</li>
					<li>Large Recessed Draining / Drip Sink</li>
					<li>Stainless Steel Waste Chute w/ Countertop Lid</li>
					<li>4 x Cutlery Drawers</li>
					<li>Crockery Storage Cupboard</li>
					<li>Pots and Pans Storage Cupboard</li>
					<li>Grocery Stowage Cupboards</li>
					<li>All Stainless Hardware has been removed and refurbished</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- DECK & EQUIPMENT -->
			<div class="s-equip__section" id="deck">
				<h2>Deck &amp; Equipment</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Windlass LOFRANS 3x 12v 1700W (2014)</li>
					<li>2 x Andersen 52ST Winch — 12V Electric</li>
					<li>2 x Andersen 46ST Winch — 12V Electric</li>
					<li>11 x 11" Aluminum Mooring Cleats and Bollard</li>
					<li>Teak Walkway Between Trampolines with Integral Anchor Chain Guide System</li>
					<li>Teak Aft Platform with Integral Dinghy Chocks</li>
					<li>Harken Mast Hardware — Battcar Track, Cars, and Blocks</li>
					<li>Spinlock Clutches</li>
					<li>Trampolines — Offshore 3/8th Polyester Open Net by Sunrise Yacht Products</li>
					<li>Boom Extension for Dinghy Lift Halyard — acts as secondary Main Halyard</li>
					<li>Zodiac 12.5' dinghy — new Hypalon tubes, new 25hp Suzuki outboard with electric start and tilt, &lt;100 hrs</li>
					<li>New weather shield for area between top of Saloon and Bimini (2022)</li>
					<li>All new outdoor cockpit cushions (Feb 2022)</li>
					<li>All Holds in floor of cockpit sanded, repainted, grate flooring added, drainage plumbing replaced/repaired</li>
					<li>Aft platform extended at considerable cost by first owners — walk past dinghy and large swim platform</li>
					<li>Carbon Fiber Vinyl Wrap around front Windows</li>
					<li>Carbon Fiber Vinyl Wrap on Bow and Stern Aluminum Crossbeams</li>
					<li>Underwater Light on Starboard Sugar Scoop</li>
					<li>New Steaming Light (Mast)</li>
					<li>New Deck Light (Mast)</li>
					<li>New VHF Antenna (Mast)</li>
				</ul>

				<h3>Steering System</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Lewmar Stainless Steel Wheel Helm with Wheel Disconnect Feature</li>
					<li>2 x Dual Chain and LewMar Cable-in-Conduit System</li>
					<li>2 x Lewmar Steering Quadrants</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- ELECTRONICS -->
			<div class="s-equip__section" id="electronics">
				<h2>Electronics &amp; Navigation</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Raymarine Axiom+ 12" MFD chartplotter (2025) — North America + Caribbean cartography, integrated with radar, AIS, and autopilot <span class="s-equip__badge s-equip__badge--new">New</span></li>
					<li>Garmin Chartplotter w/ Pantopix Forward Looking Sonar and Side Sonar (Feb 2023)</li>
					<li>Raymarine RD418HD Radome (Fall 2023)</li>
					<li>Raymarine ST60 Tridata and Wind Indicator</li>
					<li>Raymarine ST7002 Autopilot with WHITLOCI Rotary Drive</li>
					<li>Raymarine ST7002 Autopilot with LewMar Rotary Drive</li>
					<li>Raymarine X3 Autopilot Corepack</li>
					<li>Raymarine ST70 Multi-Repeater (At Interior Navigation Station)</li>
					<li>Raymarine RAY55E VHF Radio with remote Speaker in Salon</li>
					<li>Suunto Bulkhead mount Magnetic Compass</li>
					<li>2 x Raymarine GPS with External Antenna</li>
					<li>Raymarine GPS Unit</li>
					<li>Raymarine AIS650 Class B Transponder with dedicated antenna</li>
					<li>Handheld Raymarine and Icom VHF Radios</li>
					<li>Masthead Windex</li>
					<li>Windlass Remote and Chain Counter at helm</li>
					<li>Starlink satellite internet <strong>(installed by current owners)</strong></li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- AC ELECTRICAL -->
			<div class="s-equip__section" id="ac-electrical">
				<h2>AC Electrical (220VAC/120VAC)</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Original "As Built" Schematic, Wiring and Cabling Diagrams</li>
					<li>Onan 4kW Genset</li>
					<li>Victron Inverter / Charger 3000 Watt 230V (2024) <span class="s-equip__badge s-equip__badge--new">New</span></li>
					<li>Victron Multiplus 12/3000 120/50 Inverter (New 2022) <span class="s-equip__badge s-equip__badge--new">New</span></li>
					<li>Cerbo GX Touch 50 Power Management Display and control (New 2022) <span class="s-equip__badge s-equip__badge--new">New</span></li>
					<li>30amp AC Shore Power Receptacle and Cable</li>
					<li>Numerous AC Outlets in Cabins, Midships, Galley and Salon</li>
					<li>Offshore Marine G170 Galvanic Isolator</li>
					<li>AC Distribution Panel, Switches and Current Breakers</li>
					<li>New 120 volt converter in addition to the 230v</li>
					<li>115v Plugs placed and/or converted throughout the vessel</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- DC ELECTRICAL -->
			<div class="s-equip__section" id="dc-electrical">
