				<ul>
					<li>LiFePO4 Lithium 1,280Ah 12v House Battery Bank — 16 x Cells <span class="s-equip__badge s-equip__badge--upgraded">Upgraded</span></li>
					<li>2 x 400W (800W total) Solar Panels Mounted on Bimini (2022)</li>
					<li>EPEVER Tracer421SBN MPPT 40 Amp Solar Regulator with MT50 Remote Meter (2022)</li>
					<li>2x Engine Start Batteries 12V 65Ah</li>
					<li>House Bank / Engine Start batteries can be linked via Crossover Switch</li>
					<li>2 x 120amp AMPLE Alternators with Smart Regulators (Rebuilt July 2023)</li>
					<li>3 x Battery Isolator Switches</li>
					<li>Mastervolt Masterview Easy MK11 Battery Management System</li>
					<li>4 x 200AMP BMS — Programmable w/Bluetooth (Oct 2021)</li>
					<li>500Amp Over Volt Battery Protection Relay (Oct 2021)</li>
					<li>Mastershunt 500 12v Shunt and Mass Combi 100amp Battery Charger</li>
					<li>D400 12v Wind Generator</li>
					<li>Wind Generator Stop/Run Control Regulator and Dump Resistor</li>
					<li>Photocell Auto Anchor Light (On/Off Control)</li>
					<li>12v Distribution Panel, Circuit Breakers, and Fuses</li>
					<li>Thermostat Controlled 12v Cooling/Ventilation Fans</li>
					<li>12v LED Masthead Anchor, Tri Color Navigation Lights</li>
					<li>12v LED Lights in Cabin / Salon as well as Cockpit (Both Red and White)</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- PLUMBING -->
			<div class="s-equip__section" id="plumbing">
				<h2>Plumbing &amp; Water Systems</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Rainman Modular AC-140 HighOutput Watermaker — up to 37 GPH, two 40" Dow Filmtec membranes, plumbed into boat <span class="s-equip__badge s-equip__badge--new">New</span></li>
					<li>211 gallon fresh water tankage</li>
					<li>Pressurized hot and cold fresh water throughout</li>
					<li>Dometic Masterflush electric head in owner's cabin (2025)</li>
					<li>2 x Jabsco Quiet Flush Electric Toilets in guest heads</li>
					<li>Salt water spigot at galley</li>
					<li>Hand Operated Emergency Water Pump</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- SAFETY -->
			<div class="s-equip__section" id="safety">
				<h2>Safety Equipment</h2>
